This current report on Form 8-K/A amends the Current Report on Form 8-K filed by AZZ incorporated, a Texas corporation (the Company), on April 17, 2009 (the Form 8-K) to correct a clerical error contained in an exhibit filed with the Form 8-K.
Section 8  Other Events
Item 8.01.  Other Events.
On April 17, 2009, the Company filed with the Securities and Exchange Commission (the SEC) the Form 8-K, which contained as Exhibit 99.1 a presentation titled AZZ incorporated Presentation (the Presentation).  After the Company filed the Form 8-K, the Company discovered that the Presentation, as filed with the SEC, contained a clerical error on a chart in Slide 4 thereof.  A copy of Slide 4 of the Presentation, which has been corrected to remove the clerical error, is filed herewith as Exhibit 99.1.
