I surely hope that we aren't disappointed in that but it is just that because you're exactly right. I've commented on the quotation activities being good before and now I'm saying I believe it's going to start coming in now, and we feel pretty good about that in the first quarter as far as the 109.9 being a leveling point and starting to see improvement as we progress through the year and I hope that would be the case for the second quarter. As it stands right now, it appears that way.
 
 
