Section 1  Registrants Business and Operations
Item 1.01     Entry into a Material Definitive Agreement.
On January 19, 2012, AZZ Blenkhorn & Sawle Limited (B&S), a corporation existing under the laws of the Province of New Brunswick and an indirect wholly-owned subsidiary of AZZ incorporated (AZZ), entered into an Asset Purchase Agreement (the Agreement) by and among B&S, Galvan Metal, Inc., a corporation existing under the laws of Canada (Seller), and certain shareholders of Seller identified therein.  Pursuant to the Agreement, B&S will acquire substantially all of the assets of Seller, including a galvanizing plant located in Montreal, Quebec and related equipment and supplies.  The purchase price for this transaction is $29.5 million, subject to adjustment as more fully described in the Agreement.  The transaction is expected to close on or about January 31, 2012, subject to satisfaction of customary closing conditions.
The summary above does not purport to be complete and is qualified in its entirety by reference to the actual text of the Agreement, as filed as Exhibit 2.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K (incorporated herein by reference).
 
