ITEM 8.01 OTHER EVENTS
On September 27, 2012, AZZ entered into an agreement to acquire substantially all of the assets of Galvcast Manufacturing Inc. (Galvcast), a Canadian galvanizer with operations in Ontario, and certain real property owned by an affiliate of Galvcast.  AZZ would acquire these assets through AZZ Blenkhorn & Sawle Limited, an indirect wholly-owned subsidiary of AZZ.  The acquisition is expected to close on October 1, 2012, subject to the satisfaction of customary closing conditions.  AZZ announced that it had entered into this agreement in the press release attached as Exhibit 99.1.
 
