Use the proceeds of the Credit Extensions for working capital and other general corporate purposes (including to pay in part the cost of the Acquisition contemplated by the Purchase Agreement and costs and expenses incurred in connection therewith and in connection with the Loan Documents and to make Restricted Payments permitted hereby) not in contravention of any Law or of any Loan Document.
